Class PlaneSweep.KPEPlaneSweepComparator

java.lang.Object
  xxl.core.spatial.cursors.PlaneSweep.KPEPlaneSweepComparator
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparator
Enclosing class:
PlaneSweep
public static class PlaneSweep.KPEPlaneSweepComparator
extends Object
implements Comparator

Compares two Objects with respect to the first dimension of ther left borders in ascending order. This is useful for a computational geometry plane sweep. The input data is assumed to be of type KPE.

See Also:
KPE, PlaneSweep
